ry limited data availability).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0007939934730529785}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.8851225972175598}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 15, "offsetEnd": 24}, "context": "We evaluate in-VoxPopuli-domain performance with EuroParl-ST (EP) and the out-of-domain performance with CoVoST 2 We combine both corpora to train our baseline and pseudo-label 3K-hour monolingual VoxPopuli unlabeled data self-training.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994763731956482}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.0159950256347656e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 23, "offsetEnd": 32}, "context": "Transcribed speech The VoxPopuli transcribed data contains 16 languages totaling 1.8K hours and 4.3K speakers, whose detailed statistics can be found in Table 1, including duration (hours) by language, number of speakers, percentage of female speakers and number of tokens.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.6964475512504578}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.987022399902344e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 7.152557373046875e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796},