anguages, resulting in 8K-24K hours of data for each language.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0028208494186401367}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.128715515136719e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.76837158203125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 46, "offsetEnd": 55}, "context": "We observe from Table 8 that self-training on VoxPopuli improves both indomain (\"EP\") and out-of-domain (\"CV\") performance with similar magnitude most of the time.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0005696415901184082}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.87973403930664e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 48, "offsetEnd": 57}, "context": "For quick verification, we use only part of the VoxPopuli unlabeled data for pre-training.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9985338449478149}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.919269561767578e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "EuroParl-ST", "normalizedForm": "EuroParl-ST", "offsetStart": 49, "offsetEnd": 60}, "context": "We evaluate in-VoxPopuli-domain performance with EuroParl-ST (EP) and the out-of-domain performance with CoVoST 2 We combine both corpora to train our baseline and pseudo-label 3K-hour monolingual VoxPopuli unlabeled data self-training. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994763731956482}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.0159950256347656e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994763731956482}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.0159950256347656e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DeepSpeech-Polyglot", "normalizedForm": "DeepSpeech-Polyglot", "offsetStart": 49, "offsetEnd": 69}, "context": "They are compared with supervised baselines from DeepSpeech-Polyglot1 , which leverage extended CV train sets and several other corpora for training as well as LM for decoding. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00301283597946167}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0384788513183594e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00301283597946167}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0384788513183594e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 52, "offsetEnd": 61}, "context": "For quick exploration, we leverage only part of the VoxPopuli unlabeled data and leave the validation on more data to future work.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.5847427248954773}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.12034785747528076}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 53, "offsetEnd": 62}, "context": "In contrast with the political domain oral speech in VoxPopuli, they are more fluent read speech of no copyright sentences (for example, Wikipedia articles).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00020903348922729492}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.9550323486328125e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.6226043701171875e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 54, "offsetEnd": 63}, "context": "VP-Mono-5K outperforms XLSR-Mono and XLSR-10 on all 5 VoxPopuli languages (except for a tie on Es with XLSR-Mono).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.01989370584487915}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.24249267578125e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 59, "offsetEnd": 68}, "context": "To train language models (LM) for ASR decoding, we combine VoxPopuli transcription in the training set with the EuroParl corpus (Koehn, 2005), which is from the proceedings of the European Parliament from 1996 to 2011.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.8476433753967285}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0001398324966430664}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 65, "offsetEnd": 74}, "context": "We train wav2vec 2.0 models 1 on 10Khour, 50K-hour and 100K-hour VoxPopuli data in 23 languages (denoted as \"VP-10K\", \"VP-50K\" and \"VP-100K\", respectively).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.2358473539352417}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00012934207916259766}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 67, "offsetEnd": 76}, "context": "We provide VoxPopuli ASR baselines and validate the versatility of VoxPopuli unlabeled data in unsupervised representation learning and semisupervised learning for ASR as well as ST.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0001373291015625}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00022798776626586914}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-