offsetEnd": 81}, "context": "The latter is based on Common Voice v4, which has different domain than VoxPopuli and dominates the combined train set.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.03250014781951904}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00018924474716186523}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 90, "offsetEnd": 99}, "context": "The former is created from 2009-2012 EP plenary sessions and hence has the same domain as VoxPopuli.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.04050123691558838}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.008791804313659668}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 9.5367431640625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 91, "offsetEnd": 100}, "context": "For ST training with weak supervision, we combine EP, CV and 300h weakly labeled data from VoxPopuli.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.1696090698242188e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 99, "offsetEnd": 108}, "context": "We see from Table 8 that the former is on par with (or better than) the supervised baseline in the VoxPopuli domain (\"EP\") with 0.3x-1.8x", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.934720516204834}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.7523765563964844e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 103, "offsetEnd": 112}, "context": "We train Transformer Base (Vaswani et al., 2017) supervised baselines and use 0.8K/3K-hour monolingual VoxPopuli unlabeled data (from 2013-2020 sessions only to avoid overlaps with EuroParl-ST) to self-train Transformer Large models.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.3407543897628784}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 8.940696716308594e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CoVoST", "normalizedForm": "CoVoST", "offsetStart": 105, "offsetEnd": 111}, "context": "We evaluate in-VoxPopuli-domain performance with EuroParl-ST (EP) and the out-of-domain performance with CoVoST 2 We combine both corpora to train our baseline and pseudo-label 3K-hour monolingual VoxPopuli unlabeled data self-training. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994763731956482}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.0159950256347656e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994763731956482}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.0159950256347656e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Wang et al., 2020b)", "normalizedForm": "Wang et al., 2020b", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "pyannote.", "normalizedForm": "pyannote", "offsetStart": 105, "offsetEnd": 114}, "context": "To calibrate the original timestamps, we perform speaker diarization (SD) on the fullsession audio using pyannote.audio ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999074935913086}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 8.106231689453125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999074935913086}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 8.106231689453125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 111, "offsetEnd": 120}, "context": "We train CPCbased models (Riviere and Dupoux, 2020) on 500hour English and 500-hour French unlabeled data from VoxPopuli, respectively.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9592704176902771}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0709192156791687}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 115, "offsetEnd": 124}, "context": "Speech-to-speech translation models may benefit from these tactics if they are trained on interpretation data that VoxPopuli provides.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 6.35385513305664e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0010304450988769531}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 137, "offsetEnd": 146}, "context": "We conclude that multilingual representations generalize better across languages and are more robust on unseen Table 8: ST and ASR using VoxPopuli data for self-training or weak supervision.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0010961294174194336}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.1576881408691406e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999403953552246}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "VoxPopuli", "normalizedForm": "VoxPopuli", "offsetStart": 140, "offsetEnd": 149}, "context": "Interpretese vs. translationese We exemplify the differences between simultaneous oral interpretation and offline written translation using VoxPopuli in", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.6180009841918945}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.193450927734375e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999603033065796}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.999940